{"tid":2246790,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"純醫療保險討論","createTime":"2020-10-17T10:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T13:48:40.000Z","uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9aee87498eed5b2ba687d11a690e10ffb337ce5e","tid":2246790,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"細佬我曾經係一間私家醫院工作 曾經有件事係令我十分震撼<br />\n有一日我如常收症見到個病人地址應該冇5000萬都應該有1億的地址<br />\n但你估下病人揀果個CLASS係咩?<br />\nPRIVATE?NO <br />\nSEMIPRIVATE?NO<br />\nSTANDARD?BINGO!!!!!!!<br />\n由於病人年紀尚少所以有2個女人(都是典型闊太打扮(巨鑽,名錶)陪住佢 1個係佢母親 1個應該係佢親戚(當時我係咁諗,後來知道係錯的)<br />\n<br />\n果個病人住左大約5-6日到啦<br />\n呢2個女人 我都係呢5-6日不停見到 我心諗呢個丫姨真係好,好似親生媽媽咁好 因此佢係日以繼夜,夜以繼日幫手照顧呢個小朋友 <br />\n<br />\n去到第3日我見到咁,我都忍唔住同媽媽講:你真好,有這麼好的SISTER<br />\n佢跟我說:哈哈!佢係我AGENT黎架<br />\n<br />\n當時我好震撼 我終於明白咩係TOP AGENT 全身名牌又HERMES 又PP 又巨鑽係有原因 <br />\n成功係需要苦幹 而唔係蔡+賺咁玩住LEICA苦幹<br />\n同時我諗應該呢個富婆都應該同佢買左巨額人壽 個TOP AGENT先會咁SERVE佢<br />\n但同時呢個小病人只係住STANDARD CLASS (大家都明白咩原因啦~都係一個字 佣!)香港都是一個資本主義社會丫<br />\nOh..... my god 希望呢個小病人大個左唔會唔開心啦 HAHA 應該唔會的 無論咩CLASS我地同事都會好專業提供專業服務 (PROFESIIONAL IMAGE)<br />\n<br />\n好啦 故事就講到呢到<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家買醫療保險果陣 有冇試過比AGENT叫你買埋意外保,危疾保呢 或者份醫療係有儲蓄成份呢 而呢份保險又係咪真係岩你本人呢<br />\n<br />\n係香港 所有人都係錢工作 我都唔另外<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://monthly.hkej.com/monthly/article/id/2072296/%E3%80%8C%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%83%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%85%83%E8%80%81%E6%8F%AD%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmonthly.hkej.com%2Fmonthly%2Farticle%2Fid%2F2072296%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2591%2583%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%259F%25A5%25EF%25BC%2581%25E3%2580%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E9%2599%25B7&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24haoyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=3f64f94a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://monthly.hkej.com/monthly/article/id/2072296/%E3%80%8C%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%83%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%85%83%E8%80%81%E6%8F%AD%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n上面呢個新聞 唔知大家又相唔相信呢<br />\n<br />\n係香港所有代理都係靠佣金賺錢係鐵一般事實<br />\n<br />\n要AGENT而企係你地角度幫你,代表你 係冇可能的 <br />\n <br />\n而本人(多年經驗,知道唔同專科的好醫生)相反正正可以代表你幫你 因為我絕非AGENT/BROKER 向你推介相關服務後,由你自己上網投保,跟本人絕無利益關係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣請TG:qwebnm123"},{"pid":"91a884cdc2fc0750082f2f15e7c76b3bed2eab9d","tid":2246790,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"出完呢個一定會比好多AGENT/BROKER 打壓<br />\n希望大家比多D支持我"},{"pid":"ede4393abc14692f97b1beb8fbd47c1fcf2c7ffe","tid":2246790,"uid":47485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"即係點"},{"pid":"90f8479b49b64203ecc28eee37740fb9688188d7","tid":2246790,"uid":41087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"咩玩法？"},{"pid":"744ae05c4059cc5c07d1097d4c9f8b88dbc992dc","tid":2246790,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"樓主只求幫到人，大家開開心心買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac7a2775db6478440779bc4e8114651d497001e","tid":2246790,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90f8479b49b64203ecc28eee37740fb9688188d7","tid":2246790,"uid":41087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"咩玩法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"收取顧問費為客人挑選產品"},{"pid":"333515369b4633f9eefd43aabe2158056093f9fb","tid":2246790,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"744ae05c4059cc5c07d1097d4c9f8b88dbc992dc","tid":2246790,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"樓主只求幫到人，大家開開心心買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"DAMN RIGHT BRO"}]}